 zkCLEAR
 through three real-world applications. The framework faithfully follows the behavior of non-ZKP counterparts, with moderate overheads for privacy and verifiability. Additionally, we evaluate its efficiency and scalability using real-world datasets. It shows up to a 35.1× speedup in proof generation time and a 214.5× reduction in proof size compared to current general-purpose ZKP systems.
